Package: scRAS
Type: Package
Title: scRAS--measuring the rareness and anomalousness of individual cells in single-cell RNA sequencing data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Chenxing Qian
Maintainer: Chenxing Qian <qianchenxing@outlook.com>
Description: This package provides R codes for computing two measures:
    The cell state deviation (CSD) and cell anomalousness score (CAS)
    which reveal the rareness and local anomalousness of individual cells
    with respect to major populations respectively
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    Rtsne
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
